Application application = Robolectric.application
SharedPreferences sharedPreferences = PreferenceManager.getDefaultSharedPreferences(application)
Observable<java.lang.String> observable = AndroidObservable.fromSharedPreferencesChanges(sharedPreferences)
final InOrder inOrder = inOrder(observer)
inOrder.verify(observer, never()).onNext(any(java.lang.String.class))
sharedPreferences.edit().putBoolean("a", true).commit()
inOrder.verify(observer, times(1)).onNext("a")
sharedPreferences.edit().putInt("b", 9).commit()
inOrder.verify(observer, times(1)).onNext("a")
sharedPreferences.edit().putInt("c", 42).commit()
inOrder.verify(observer, never()).onNext(any(java.lang.String.class))
inOrder.verify(observer, never()).onError(any(java.lang.Throwable.class))
inOrder.verify(observer, never()).onCompleted()
